description: The fund is an actively managed exchange-traded fund (“ETF”) that employs proprietary trend-based and sector rotation strategies developed by the fund’s investment sub-adviser. The fund invests in shares of other ETFs based on a rules-based process managed by the sub-adviser that reflects a blend of the sub-adviser’s trend-based and sector rotation strategies. The fund is non-diversified.
name: McElhenny Sheffield Managed Risk ETF
